   • ‘minor-mode’
   • ‘multi-category’
   • ‘package’
   • ‘project-file’
   • ‘symbol’ (the ‘describe-symbol’ command bound to ‘C-h o’)
   • ‘theme’
   • ‘unicode-name’ (the ‘insert-char’ command bound to ‘C-x 8 RET’)
